ng-widest'>Portal Preview</h2><p class='text-sm text-stone-500 leading-relaxed font-medium'>Step into your customer's world. Preview the complete journey with the latest architectural layout.</p></div><button onclick='Peera.dev.launch()' class='w-full py-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-[30px] text-[11px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-all active:scale-95 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-600/30 hover:shadow-blue-600/50'>Launch Portal</button></div></div></div><div class='mt-24 pt-10 border-t border-stone-200 dark:border-white/10 flex justify-between items-center'><div class='flex items-center gap-4'><div class='w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-ping absolute'></div><div class='w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full relative'></div><span class='text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-stone-950 dark:text-white opacity-40'>System Status: Verified</span></div><div class='flex gap-8'><span class='text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-stone-400 hover:text-stone-950 dark:hover:text-white cursor-pointer transition-colors'>Documentation</span><span onclick='Peera.dev.toggle()' class='text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-red-500/50 hover:text-red-500 cursor-pointer transition-colors'>Emergency Kill-Switch</span></div></div></div></div>"
